data.description: 5K BUYER INCENTIVE TO USE TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS, INTEREST RATE BUYDOWN, OR HOWEVER YOU WOULD LIKE! Moore schools!! This 3 bed, 2 and a half bath home is just waiting for its next owner. With over 2,100sq ft, including 2 dining areas and 2 living areas, this home has ample room to entertain. It is filled with charming features including cute plantation shutters, built-ins around the fireplace and a built-in hutch with tons of storage in the kitchen. Enjoy the covered porch in your fenced backyard. Additionally, a front courtyard offers a unique space where your creativity can flourish - turn it into a beautiful garden or a cozy sitting area to welcome guests. Underground storm shelter in garage.
